 {
 if : 
======================
 if(condition){ if condition is satisfy then go to the next line of execution
 statements; //execute this statement
 }
 
 if...else
 
 if(condition){ if satify then go the next line and execute the statement 
 statement;
 }else  // if condition is not satisfy then execute the statement present in else block 
 {
 statement;
 }